channel.title: Crashing when teleporting to Ardy, Fala and Tzhaar cave
channel.description:
Whenever i teleport to Ardy, Fala or the tzhaar cave the person crashs until i go into the file and changes the coords of the player to another place like lumbridge. I don't know why but i really need the player to be able to go these places. Please help me, feel free to ask questions that may help you understanding and solving the problem.
Thank you.
